overview: The Three Musketeers tells the story of Eddy. A lanky young man who follows in his father's footsteps by joining a passionate musketeers club. Eddy quickly makes a name for himself as the new d'Artagnan. He acts out this part with passionate conviction. As the peer pressure intensifies Eddy identity clashes with his alter ego d'Artagnan. Will he manage to navigate his way out of this dangerous game?
title: The Three Musketeers
